There are several persistent conditions that are appropriate to take at character creation. Players may wish to consider: Adult Supervision, Body Dysmorphia, Embarrassing Phylactery, Heartfelt Vow, Name of the Moon, Slow Transformation, Two Hearts One Soul or Unstable Transformation. 

